Once users have credits, they should be able to redeem them. Checking the balance involves loading the most recent balance from the server and then reading the balance. These can be two separate steps but for the sake of simplicity we have combined them into one example:    iOS - Swift  Branch . getInstance (). loadRewards   {   ( changed ,   error )   in 
